name: Simpler Times
description: We used to sit aside the fire, listening to ducks in their weightless choir. Nothing was from us required other than rest cause we were oh so tired. "Things may go uphill from now yet quitting you will not allow. Further I'll no longer go, but you will take me in your corazon." That was said and it was so, up the hills and valleys low, always felt you with me close, though never closer than before.
